---
// MainMethod.astro - Displays the main methodology figure for WestWorld
---
<section id="methodology" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Methodology</h2>

    <div class="figure-container">
      <img src="/main.png" alt="WestWorld framework overview" class="main-figure" />
      <p class="figure-caption">
        <strong>Figure 1: WestWorld Framework Overview.</strong>
        The overall architecture of our proposed WestWorld, consisting of two core components: (a) a <span class="insight-highlight">Knowledge-Encoded Embedding Module</span> that injects structural embeddings as an inductive bias into trajectory representations, and (b) a <span class="insight-highlight">System-aware MoE block</span> that models diverse system dynamics via system-aware expert routing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .figure-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem auto;
  }

  .main-figure {
    max-width: 90%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .figure-caption {
    text-align: left;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .figure-caption strong {
    color: #2a2f6c;
  }

  .insight-highlight {
    color: #059669;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
